---
title: Honey & Thyme-Glazed Halloumi & Beef Rump with Garlicky Veggie Couscous & Garlic Yoghurt
description: There was complete mayhem when this dish hit our tasting table. With sweet honey and fragrant thyme on warm, salty halloumi, plus roasted chunks of veggies scattered through fluffy couscous, it disappeared from the bowl in record time. Enjoy!

